{"tid":1992642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"抗暴之戰】曾遭警暴打斷腳 男生認搬單車堵路 今准簽保守行為了事","createTime":"2020-04-28T09:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T00:22:08.000Z","uid":19287,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e337644fe3ce7ee50b099a3cf7fdca2c1669af11","tid":1992642,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:20:50.000Z","msg":"網民去年11月連日發起三罷及堵路行動，男學生於去年11月發起三罷及堵路行動中，在將軍澳隧道公路上搬運共享單車企圖堵路，惟遭巡警制服。男生事後被控，提堂時左腳小腿裝上支架，據知是在被捕時遭警圍毆打斷腳骨。他今於觀塘裁判法院獲撤控，准以自簽2,000元、守行為12個月了事，並須繳付1,000元堂費。<br />\n<br />\n#抗暴之戰<br />\n【曾遭警暴打斷腳 男生認搬單車堵路 今准簽保守行為了事】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zF3W4Z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zF3W4Z&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=2450500f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zF3W4Z</a>"},{"pid":"5f19af0c9f744595b318083dc3fc84c141230e4b","tid":1992642,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"近排支那想吹和風"},{"pid":"63d00a44d5247fe789bcd463eb8767c0b3e622a4","tid":1992642,"uid":88743,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:23:40.000Z","msg":"唔想搞大就撤控<br />\n好彩佢係斷腳骨<br />\n如果係碎頭蓋骨應該變左自殺數字"},{"pid":"b9d250b37876334d86c4cab7f089a99554b22906","tid":1992642,"uid":55598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:24:32.000Z","msg":"撤控咗仲要守行爲？"},{"pid":"98a2af0372253110890d2a008c58b31962a02262","tid":1992642,"uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:25:00.000Z","msg":"又冇得追究斷腳個損失屌佢老母"},{"pid":"c7151e97fc75f4892696aa1922ed6b239f9082d1","tid":1992642,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98a2af0372253110890d2a008c58b31962a02262","tid":1992642,"uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:25:00.000Z","msg":"又冇得追究斷腳個損失屌佢老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:25:53.000Z","msg":"exactly!"},{"pid":"82187671a2f111a763ac381a38b7ebdd09453901","tid